metadata.description:
Written, arranged, produced, and performed by Weinbagz. Mastered by Genzo Rubin. 

I wrote this track in late 2022. It was a very challenging time for me mentally. I was going through a lot of IRL issues and my life felt like it was being turned upside down. The lyrics for this track sort of slipped out effortlessly, and really came from the pain I was feeling. 

I remember spending every night trying to make things feel right yet it never quite worked, and the issues that I was facing really felt like they were hitting home. Home is a very important concept to me and the feeling of home can instantly vanish, which is a hard thing to confront and accept.

This track was my way of trying to express my pain and make things feel right again.

lyrics.text:
Hitting it home
Hitting it home yea
Hitting it home woah
Hit it home with me baby

I just can't help myself tonight
Gotta push it through
I'm trying to make it all feel right
Like I always Do

metadata.name: Like I Always Do #1
metadata.title: Like I Always Do
